s used in our simulations. Our results are qualitatively\nconsistent with the observed hard X-ray emissions in solar flares.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Apr 2012 16:18:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 May 2012 15:10:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
