 and with an effective frequency which scales\nnonlinearly with wavenumber. Taking the usual inflationary parameters we find\nthat the frequency of the oscillations is so large as to render the effect\ndifficult to observe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Apr 2012 00:26:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 May 2012 13:25:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-30"}
