al temperature. We discuss\nthe results in the context of re-condensation of coronal material in the inner\nregion of the disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Apr 2012 03:31:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
