ts toward the possibility\nthat the $\\rho$ meson could transform as part of an antisymmetric tensor with\nan $a_{1}$ meson-like state as its representation companion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Apr 2012 11:10:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Jul 2012 19:38:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-04"}
